# Insider Wallets

Insiders are wallets connected to the project creator.

They usually receive tokens **before the public launch**.

Too many insiders can be dangerous.

---

## Why Insider Tokens Are Risky

If insiders hold large amounts:

They can sell suddenly and crash the price.

This is one of the most common causes of rug pulls.

---

## Healthy Distribution

Look for coins where:

• no wallet owns an excessive percentage
• tokens are distributed across many holders.

A well distributed coin is safer.

---

