# Lesson 4.3

# Sniper Bots

Snipers are bots that buy the coin **milliseconds after launch**.

These bots try to capture the cheapest prices.

But too many snipers can damage a project.

---

## Why Snipers Are Dangerous

When bots control large amounts of tokens:

They may sell quickly for profit.

This creates sudden crashes.

---

## Healthy Launch Pattern

A healthy coin shows:

• gradual buying activity
• organic wallet growth
• multiple buyers.

Not one wallet dominating early trades.

---

## Action Exercise

