# Holder Distribution

Holder distribution tells you **who owns the supply**.

Good distribution means:

• many holders
• small individual positions.

Bad distribution means:

• a few wallets control most tokens.

---

## Red Flag Distribution

Danger signals include:

• top wallet holding huge supply
• top 10 wallets controlling majority of tokens.

This creates selling pressure.

---

## Healthy Coin Signals

Look for:

• growing holder count
• diversified ownership.

More holders means **stronger community growth**.

---

