# Lesson 4.5

# Real vs Fake Volume

Volume is one of the most important indicators.

But not all volume is real.

Some tokens generate **fake volume**.

---

## Fake Volume Signs

Warning signals include:

• repeated identical trades
• suspicious patterns
• extremely fast buy-sell cycles.

These may indicate **bot activity**.

---

## Organic Volume Signals

Healthy volume shows:

• many different buyers
• consistent growth
• varied transaction sizes.

